---
title: Cheesy Bacon & Asparagus Strata with Tuscan Home Fries & Balsamic Arugula Salad | Serves 4 ($8.75/serving)
description: We can’t think of a better way to honor the best mom in your life than this delicious Mother’s Day brunch. That’s why this year, we’re sending everything you need to make a restaurant-worthy meal at home—so you can focus on the great food and company, and forget about making reservations. You’ll start with an oh-so melty, cheesy bacon and asparagus strata. Crispy breakfast-style potatoes served up on the side make this a one-of-a-kind, mom-umental meal.
